<item>
            <title>[LU-8443] Can&apos;t create Lustre FS with enabled meta_bg option</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8443</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@devvm-sl6-1 MRP-3473&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# mkfs.lustre --ost --fsname=testfs --mountfsoptions=&apos;meta_bg&apos; --mkfsoptions=&quot;-O meta_bg,^resize_inode&quot; --reformat  --index=0 --mgsnode=172.0.0.1 /dev/sdb1&lt;br/&gt;
mkfs.lustre: Warning: default mount option `errors=remount-ro&apos; is missing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   Permanent disk data:&lt;br/&gt;
Target:     testfs:OST0000&lt;br/&gt;
Index:      0&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre FS:  testfs&lt;br/&gt;
Mount type: ldiskfs&lt;br/&gt;
Flags:      0x62&lt;br/&gt;
              (OST first_time update )&lt;br/&gt;
Persistent mount opts: meta_bg&lt;br/&gt;
Parameters: mgsnode=172.0.0.1@tcp&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;device size = 2046MB&lt;br/&gt;
formatting backing filesystem ldiskfs on /dev/sdb1&lt;br/&gt;
    target name  testfs:OST0000&lt;br/&gt;
    4k blocks     523915&lt;br/&gt;
    options        -J size=81 -I 256 -q -O meta_bg,^resize_inode,extents,uninit_bg,dir_nlink,quota,huge_file,flex_bg -G 256 -E resize=4290772992,lazy_journal_init,lazy_itable_init=0 -F&lt;br/&gt;
mkfs_cmd = mke2fs -j -b 4096 -L testfs:OST0000  -J size=81 -I 256 -q -O meta_bg,^resize_inode,extents,uninit_bg,dir_nlink,quota,huge_file,flex_bg -G 256 -E resize=4290772992,lazy_journal_init,lazy_itable_init=0 -F /dev/sdb1 523915&lt;br/&gt;
mkfs.lustre: Can&apos;t make configs dir /tmp/mntWBthZy/CONFIGS (Input/output error)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Message from syslogd@devvm-sl6-1 at Jun 30 14:00:49 ...&lt;br/&gt;
 kernel:journal commit I/O error&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mkfs.lustre FATAL: failed to write local files&lt;br/&gt;
mkfs.lustre: exiting with -1 (Unknown error 18446744073709551615)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
